'''Igelmimen Imeqranen''' (s [[tanglizit]]: ''Great Lakes''; s tefrensist: ''Grands Lacs''), d igelmimen n waman iẓidanen ay d-yezgan deg ugafa-agmuḍan (nord-est) n [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Temrikt n Ugafa]], ɣef tlisa gar [[Kanada]] ed [[Iwunak Yeddukklen|Yiwunak Yeddukklen]]. Llan semmus (5) n yigelmimen imeqranen: [[Agelmim n Superior]], [[agelmim n Michigan]], [[agelmim n Huron]], [[agelmim n Erie]] akked win n [[Ontario]]. D ta ay d tagrawt tameqrant akk n yigelmimen seg yidis n tjumma (superficie), yerna tajumma-nsen, s ujemmal, tuweḍ ɣer 208.610 km2 (yikilumitren imkuẓen, ma d ableɣ (volume) n waman-nsen yuweḍ ɣer 22.560 km3 (yikilumitren igasasen). Igelmimen Imeqranen jemɛen 21% seg waman iẓidanen n umaḍal.

